What is a WebService? 




Types of WebServices

1.SOAP ->>> Simple Object Access Protocol works over the HTTP with the help of the internet.
2.REST --?>>> Representational Stateful APIs



	Differences between SOAP and REST


	SOAP Request                                                                   REST REquest

	1.Endpoint URL                                                                 1.Endpoint URL
	http://www.xyz.com/login                                                        http://www.xyz.com/login
	http://www.xyz.com/createAccount
	http://www.xyz.com/getEmployeeList

